Detailed Description

template<int DIM>
class SAMRAI::math::PatchEdgeDataOpsInteger< DIM >

Class PatchEdgeDataOpsInteger<DIM> provides a collection of operations that may be used to manipulate integer edge-centered patch data. The operations include basic arithmetic, min, max, etc. With the exception of a few basic routines, this class inherits its interface (and thus its functionality) from the base class PatchEdgeDataBasicOps<DIM> from which it is derived.

A more extensive set of operations is implemented for real (double and float) and complex patch data in the classes PatchEdgeDataOpsReal<DIM> and PatchEdgeDataOpsComplex<DIM>, repsectively.

See also:
math::PatchEdgeDataBasicOps
